text.tspan: HehtorOCH is a mid 2.0 male scratcher.
Once was a noticeable face back in 2018
who had recognition from his animated series
"TWOHHS", who has now fallen from his
fame. Hehtor is an underrated scratcher who
makes high quality animations and was a
highly known user back in his past.
